《'''誰殺了大個子'''》（{{lang-en|''City of Lies''}}）是一部2018年美國犯罪電影，由{{link-en|布萊德·福爾曼|Brad Furman}}擔任編劇執導，[[強尼·戴普|強尼·戴普]]及[[科力士·韋德加|科力士·韋德加]]主演<ref>{{Cite web|title=《誰殺了大個子》延宕2年台灣確定4/1上映、強尼戴普聯手佛瑞斯惠特克狂飆演技！|url=https://times.hinet.net/mobile/news/23255400|accessdate=2021-03-29|date=2021-03-14|work=HiNet生活誌}}</ref>

==發行==
這部電影的第一部預告片最初名為LAbyrinth，於2018年5月21日發行，這將是臭名昭著的B.I.G.的46歲生日。<ref>{{Cite web|title=New trailer for Johnny Depp/Forest Whitaker murder mystery City of Lies now online|url=https://www.filmfetish.com/2018/05/21/new-trailer-for-johnny-depp-forest-whitaker-murder-mystery-city-of-lies-now-online/|accessdate=2021-05-01|date=2018-05-21|last=Carson|first=Maria F.|work=https://www.filmfetish.com/2018/05/21/new-trailer-for-johnny-depp-forest-whitaker-murder-mystery-city-of-lies-now-online/|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-05-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210501114128/https://www.filmfetish.com/2018/05/21/new-trailer-for-johnny-depp-forest-whitaker-murder-mystery-city-of-lies-now-online/|dead-url=no}}</ref>在[[开路影业|開路影業]]和{{le|IM Global|IM Global}}合併組成[[开路影业|Global Road Entertainment]]之後，該電影改名為《誰殺了大個子》，並於2018年9月7日發行，這是{{le|Tupac Shakur被謀殺22週年|Murder of Tupac Shakur}}。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Johnny Depp’s ‘City of Lies’ Acquired for China|url=https://variety.com/2018/film/asia/johnny-depps-city-of-lies-acquired-for-china-1202805028/|accessdate=2021-05-01|date=2018-05-09|last=Frater|first=Patrick|work=Variety|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-05-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210501113517/https://variety.com/2018/film/asia/johnny-depps-city-of-lies-acquired-for-china-1202805028/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Johnny Depp is investigating 2Pac and Biggie's murder in this new trailer for City of Lies|url=https://filmindustry.network/johnny-depp-is-investigating-2pac-and-biggies-murder-in-this-new-trailer-for-city-of-lies/33023|accessdate=2021-05-01|date=2018-05-21|work=Film Industry Network|language=en-US}}</ref>據報導，由於Depp和電影的經理位置正在進行的訴訟，電影於2018年8月被取消上映，但沒有宣布更換日期。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Johnny Depp’s ‘City Of Lies’ Movie Pulled From Release Schedule|url=https://deadline.com/2018/08/city-of-lies-johnny-depp-movie-pulled-release-schedule-1202441341/|accessdate=2021-05-01|date=2018-08-06|last=Hipes|first=Patrick|work=Deadline|language=en-US|archive-date=2018-08-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180825003744/https://deadline.com/2018/08/city-of-lies-johnny-depp-movie-pulled-release-schedule-1202441341/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2018年8月23日，[[每日野獸|每日野獸]]報導強尼·戴普被當作替代羔羊。它表明洛杉磯警察局可能一直在試圖壓制這部被負面描寫的電影，或者還有其他主要參與者不希望這部電影上映。<ref>{{Cite news|title=Inside the Shocking Death of Johnny Depp’s Biggie-Murder Movie ‘City of Lies’|url=https://www.thedailybeast.com/inside-the-shocking-death-of-johnny-depps-biggie-murder-movie-city-of-lies|newspaper=The Daily Beast|date=2018-08-23|accessdate=2021-05-01|language=en|first=Justin|last=Rohrlich|archive-date=2021-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210305035349/https://www.thedailybeast.com/inside-the-shocking-death-of-johnny-depps-biggie-murder-movie-city-of-lies|dead-url=no}}</ref>2020年7月，亞當·托德·布朗（Adam Tod Brown）辯稱，這部電影被壓制了，因此沃萊塔·華萊士（Voletta Wallace）無法重新開放{{le|臭名昭著的B.I.G.起訴LAPD的謀殺案|Murder of the Notorious B.I.G.}}。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Banned Media Report: City Of Lies by Conspiracy! The Show • A podcast on Anchor|url=https://anchor.fm/conspiracytheshow/episodes/Banned-Media-Report-City-Of-Lies-egsrl0|accessdate=2021-05-01|work=Anchor|language=en|archive-date=2021-05-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210502003348/https://anchor.fm/conspiracytheshow/episodes/Banned-Media-Report-City-Of-Lies-egsrl0|dead-url=no}}</ref>在2018年8月29日，[[以色列国民银行|以色列國民銀行]]又對[[米拉麥克斯影業|米拉麥克斯影業]]提起了另一項訴訟，要求賠償因撤消影片而導致的數百萬美元的未付保證金。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Global Road, Miramax Sued by Bank Over Refusal to Release 'City of Lies'|url=https://www.thewrap.com/global-road-miramax-sued-by-bank-over-refusal-to-releasecity-of-lies/|accessdate=2021-05-01|date=2018-08-30|work=TheWrap|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-05-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210505171324/https://www.thewrap.com/global-road-miramax-sued-by-bank-over-refusal-to-releasecity-of-lies/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

誰殺了大個子於2018年12月9日在{{le|意大利電影節|Courmayeur Noir Film Festival}}上首映，當時是非競賽片，是該電影的閉幕電影，在電影節的Noir上亮相。<ref>{{Cite web|title=CITY OF LIES - L’ORA DELLA VERITÀ. Film di chiusura fuori concorso|url=http://www.noirfest.com/2018/Concorso.asp?id_dettaglio=1298&lang=|accessdate=2021-05-01|last=Coop|first=Studio|work=Noir in Festival|language=en|archive-date=2021-05-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210501131253/http://www.noirfest.com/2018/Concorso.asp?id_dettaglio=1298&lang=|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=[Noir in Festival] Recensione di City of lies - L'ora della verità, con Johnny Depp • Universal Movies|url=https://www.universalmovies.it/noir-in-festival-recensione-di-city-of-lies-lora-della-verita-con-johnny-depp/|accessdate=2021-05-01|language=it|archive-date=2021-05-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210501065516/https://www.universalmovies.it/noir-in-festival-recensione-di-city-of-lies-lora-della-verita-con-johnny-depp/|dead-url=no}}</ref>它於2019年1月10日獲得了限量發行。這部電影於2019年6月19日在意大利的[[藍光光碟|藍光光碟]]發行。<ref>{{Citation|title=City of Lies Blu-ray Release Date June 19, 2019|url=https://www.blu-ray.com/movies/City-of-Lies-Blu-ray/244708/|accessdate=2021-05-01|archive-date=2021-05-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210502142436/https://www.blu-ray.com/movies/City-of-Lies-Blu-ray/244708/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

{{le|Sagan電影公司|Saban Capital Group}}於2021年3月4日宣布已接管發行權，併計劃在2021年3月19日上映該電影。<ref>{{Cite web|title=City of Lies: Johnny Depp's Notorious B.I.G. movie hits theaters in 2 weeks|url=https://www.joblo.com/movie-news/city-of-lies-johnny-depp-notorious-big-movie|accessdate=2021-05-01|date=2021-03-04|work=www.joblo.com|archive-date=2021-05-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210505163102/https://www.joblo.com/movie-news/city-of-lies-johnny-depp-notorious-big-movie|dead-url=no}}</ref>由於與[[COVID-19|COVID-19]]大流行相關的限制，許多電影院場館仍然關閉。

==製作==
[[File:Johnny_Depp_2,_2011.jpg|thumb]]
2013年2月4日，Miriam Segal的英國製片公司Good Films購買了{{le|Randall Sullivan|Randall Sullivan}}的非小說類書籍LAbyrinth的電影版權。此電影探究了[[洛杉磯|洛杉磯]]警方的腐敗行為，這與偵探{{le|拉塞爾·普爾|Russell Poole}}對[[圖帕克·夏庫爾|圖帕克·夏庫爾]]和[[聲名狼藉先生|聲名狼藉先生]]謀殺案的調查有關，但從未得到解決。<ref>{{Cite web|title=U.K.'s Good Films Buys Rights to L.A. Cop Corruption Novel 'LAbyrinth'|url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/good-films-buys-novel-labyrinth-417756|accessdate=2021-05-01|date=2013-02-04|work=The Hollywood Reporter|language=en|archive-date=2021-05-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210501061640/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/good-films-buys-novel-labyrinth-417756|dead-url=no}}</ref>據報導，[[強尼·戴普|強尼·戴普]]於2016年9月7日在影片中扮演洛杉磯警察偵探普爾的角色。<ref name="#1">{{Cite web|title=Johnny Depp to Star in Notorious B.I.G.-Tupac Thriller 'Labyrinth'|url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/johnny-depp-star-notorious-big-926183|accessdate=2021-05-01|date=2016-09-07|work=The Hollywood Reporter|language=en|archive-date=2021-05-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210501130912/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/johnny-depp-star-notorious-big-926183|dead-url=no}}</ref>

[[布拉德·福爾曼|布拉德·福爾曼]]由克里斯蒂安·孔特雷拉斯（Christian Contreras）撰寫並改編自該書。<ref name="#1"/>9月19日，[[開路影業|開路影業]]獲得了該電影在美國的發行權。它與[[米拉麥克斯影業|米拉麥克斯影業]]共同資助了這部電影，而{{le|Good Universe|Good Universe}}則負責該電影的國際銷售。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Open Road Acquires Johnny Depp Crime Thriller ‘Labyrinth’|url=https://variety.com/2016/film/news/johnny-depp-crime-thriller-labyrinth-open-road-1201865154/|accessdate=2021-05-01|date=2016-09-19|last=Kroll|first=Justin|work=Variety|language=en-US|archive-date=2016-12-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161225154426/http://variety.com/2016/film/news/johnny-depp-crime-thriller-labyrinth-open-road-1201865154/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

===演員===
2016年11月11日，[[洛克蒙·鄧巴|洛克蒙·鄧巴]]在電影中飾演長發s（Dreadlocks）。當天，[[科力士·韋德加|科力士·韋德加]]宣布參與了這部電影，扮演了與警察合作揭露真相的新聞記者。11月17日，{{le|尼爾·布朗|Neil Brown Jr.}}在影片中扮演警察{{le|拉斐爾·佩雷斯|Rafael Pérez (police officer)}}的角色。[[山德·貝克利|山德·貝克利]]、[[希亞·溫漢|希亞·溫漢]]、{{le|Wynn Everett|Wynn Everett}}和[[托比·哈斯|托比·哈斯]]於12月13日加入劇組，兩天后，{{le|Louis Herthum|Louis Herthum}}和{{le|Shamier Anderson|Shamier Anderson}}也加入了劇組，Herthum扮演一名城市律師，在審判中為Poole辯護，Anderson扮演腐敗LAPD軍官{{le|拉斐爾·佩雷斯|Rafael Pérez (police officer)}}。<ref>{{Cite web|title=‘LAbyrinth’ Adds To Its Cast As Production Begins; Shioli Kutsuna Joins ‘The Outsider’|url=https://deadline.com/2016/12/labyrinth-cast-production-begins-shioli-kutsuna-the-outsider-1201869641/|accessdate=2021-05-01|date=2016-12-14|last=N'Duka|first=Amanda|work=Deadline|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-05-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210503132332/https://deadline.com/2016/12/labyrinth-cast-production-begins-shioli-kutsuna-the-outsider-1201869641/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Louis Herthum & Shamier Anderson Cast In ‘LAbyrinth’|url=https://deadline.com/2016/12/louis-herthum-shamier-anderson-johnny-depp-labyrinth-movie-1201870539/|accessdate=2021-05-01|date=2016-12-15|last=N'Duka|first=Amanda|work=Deadline|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-05-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210502055313/https://deadline.com/2016/12/louis-herthum-shamier-anderson-johnny-depp-labyrinth-movie-1201870539/|dead-url=no}}</ref>在2017年1月6日，{{le|阿明·約瑟夫|Amin Joseph}}加入電影，飾演警察{{le|凱文·蓋恩斯|Kevin Gaines (police officer)}}，並在1月18日，{{le|勞倫斯·梅森|Laurence Mason}}扮演聯邦調查局特工鄧頓（Dunton）。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Amin Joseph Cast In ‘LAbyrinth’; Shioli Kutsuna Joins Indie Film ‘Oh Lucy!’|url=https://deadline.com/2017/01/amin-joseph-labyrinth-johnny-depp-shioli-kutsuna-josh-hartnett-oh-lucy-film-1201880207/|accessdate=2021-05-01|date=2017-01-07|last=N'Duka|first=Amanda|work=Deadline|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-05-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210505084433/https://deadline.com/2017/01/amin-joseph-labyrinth-johnny-depp-shioli-kutsuna-josh-hartnett-oh-lucy-film-1201880207/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=‘Soldado’ Cast ‘Teen Wolf’ Actor Ian Bohen; Laurence Mason Boards ‘LAbyrinth’|url=https://deadline.com/2017/01/soldado-ian-bohen-laurence-mason-labyrinth-movie-1201889040/|accessdate=2021-05-01|date=2017-01-18|last=N'Duka|first=Amanda|work=Deadline|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-05-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210501061641/https://deadline.com/2017/01/soldado-ian-bohen-laurence-mason-labyrinth-movie-1201889040/|dead-url=no}}</ref>2017年1月23日，新人約瑟夫·費蘭特（Joseph Ferrante）參加了這部電影，擔任未公開的角色。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Netflix’s ‘Come Sunday’ Adds Stacey Sargeant; Joseph Ferrante Cast In ‘LAbyrinth’|url=https://deadline.com/2017/01/netflixs-come-sunday-stacey-sergeant-joseph-ferrante-labyrinth-movie-1201892097/|accessdate=2021-05-01|date=2017-01-23|last=N'Duka|first=Amanda|work=Deadline|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-05-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210503002656/https://deadline.com/2017/01/netflixs-come-sunday-stacey-sergeant-joseph-ferrante-labyrinth-movie-1201892097/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

